section.def:
committee
                (委員會) means the Social Work Training Fund
            Committee established by section 5;

fund
                (基金) means the Social Work Training Fund
            established by section 3;

secretary
                (秘書) means the secretary of the committee
            appointed under section 7;

paragraph.content:
in making grants to individuals for the purpose of study and training as
                    social workers, including payment of passages, travel and subsistence allowances
                    and other incidental expenses;
